Building the Foundation


What are your responsibilities and how does your role fit within the team and organization?

What are your expectations of me and my role?

What are your career objectives?

What are the three biggest things that I can do to help you?

What are the team’s strengths and weaknesses? What are yours?



Understanding Personality and Work Style/Preferences


What is the path that led you to this team?

How do you prefer I communicate with you (e.g., e-mail, phone, in-person)?

How do you like to be approached regarding an issue or challenge?



Exceling in My New Role


What are you looking forward to as I step into this role?

What are your greatest concerns as I step into this role?

What are my day-to-day responsibilities? What do you view as the challenges/pain points of my role?

What general advice or guidance do you have for me?

How will my performance be measured during my transition and beyond?

Do you have a sense of how the team might be able to score a “quick win”?

What insight do you have on my manager’s style, “hot buttons,” challenges?
